# Green Tree Web3 Concept - Environment Configuration
# Production data configuration. No private key or wallet secret belongs here.

# Server-only Solana RPC used for token state, balances and recent transactions.
# Use a dedicated Mainnet endpoint in production. Never expose API keys through NEXT_PUBLIC_*.
